-- Redecard to Invest About 500 Million Reais in 2012
-- B y   F r a n c i s c o   M a r c e l i n o
-- 2012-02-02T11:07:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-02/redecard-to-invest-about-500-million-reais-in-2012-correct-.html
Redecard SA (RDCD3)  plans to invest about 500
million reais in 2012, Chief Financial Officer Marcelo Kopel
told reporters today in  Sao Paulo .  The company invested 218 million reais in 2011, Chief
Executive Officer Claudio Yamaguti said at the same press
conference.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Francisco Marcelino in Sao Paulo at 
